players.plus:
[{
    "text": "Great rebounder with strong hands who boxes out, hustles out of his area, and has a good nose for the ball.",
"media": "img/media/c_swanigan_great_rebounder.gif"
  },
  {
    "text": "Good shooter off the pick-and-pop, spot-ups, and free throws. Has a quick release. He’ll need to extend to NBA range, though.",
"media": "img/media/c_swanigan_good_shooter.gif"
  },
  {
    "text": "Conditioning improved in college, which helped him sustain his production late in games as fatigue set in."
  },
  {
    "text": "Versatile interior scorer who uses his wide frame to carve out space and both hands to finish. Can also facilitate from the post."
}]

