  {
"text": "Defensive liability, especially in pick-and-roll. Doesn’t slide his feet well on the perimeter and lacks verticality to contest at the rim.",
"media": "img/media/c_swanigan_defensive_liability.gif"
  },
  {
"text": "Athletic limitations put a cap on his defensive upside even if his fundamentals and awareness improve."
  }]

