  },
  {
    "text": "At his best going downhill, and can navigate pick-and-roll well. Has upside as a screen-game threat if his shot translates."
  },
  {
    "text": "Defensive upside is there, despite his flaws. He has a thick, muscular frame with a solid wingspan. Great rebounder."
