  {
    "text": "Shooting issues: slow shooting release and one-two step that leads to blocked shots. Poor free throw shooter.",
    "media": "img/media/o_anunoby_shooting_issues.gif"
  } ,
{
    "text": "Lacks fluidity transitioning dribble into shot due to rigid mechanics."
  }]

