players.plus:
  [{
    "text": "Fluid athlete who finishes well in transition and on cuts. NBA spacing will aid his ability to drive in a straight line to the rim."
  },
  {
    "text": "Great shooting upside; can splash 3s off screens and dribble handoffs, and he excels on spot-ups. Needs a quicker release though.",
